description: If you’re craving some smoked meats, but could also go for a big burrito, Pappa Ralphie’s has got you covered with their terrifically tasty BBQ infused Mexican food. This bustling truck is serving up a variety of tacos, burritos, quesadillas, and more, all brimming with scrumptious chicken, pork, and beef, seasoned to perfection, and smoked right in the Pappa Ralphie’s trailer. This delicious food is perfect for parties, festivals, and events, and wherever you are in Colorado, Pappa Ralphie’s is happy to come to you and provide the goods.
name: Pappa Ralphie's
